            <paragraph>Slows down the vehicle by applying a braking force. The vehicle is only slowed down if the wheels are in contact with a surface. The force you need to apply to adequately slow down your vehicle depends on the <reference internal="True" refuri="class_rigidbody3d#class-rigidbody3d-property-mass"><inline classes="std std-ref">RigidBody3D.mass</inline></reference> of the vehicle. For a vehicle with a mass set to 1000, try a value in the 25 - 30 range for hard braking.</paragraph>
