            <paragraph>The steering angle for the vehicle. Setting this to a non-zero value will result in the vehicle turning when it's moving. Wheels that have <reference internal="True" refuri="class_vehiclewheel3d#class-vehiclewheel3d-property-use-as-steering"><inline classes="std std-ref">VehicleWheel3D.use_as_steering</inline></reference> set to <literal>true</literal> will automatically be rotated.</paragraph>
            <paragraph><strong>Note:</strong> This property is edited in the inspector in degrees. In code the property is set in radians.</paragraph>
